Package Vehicle

Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
Vehicle.Vehicle
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bus, Car, Truck
public abstract class Vehicle extends Object
An abstract representation of a vehicle, providing a foundation for specific vehicle types within the simulation. This class encapsulates common attributes and behaviors that all vehicles share, such as movement capabilities, physical characteristics, and status attributes like reputation and damage.
